    "followRuleId": "953571076070313984",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"margin-left: -0.5pt; background: white; border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 2;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 697.4pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" width=\"930\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">特殊资质/要求</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 697.4pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; background: transparent; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" width=\"930\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">营业执照经营范围需包含&ldquo;互联网信息服务&rdquo;或&ldquo;信息网络传播视听节目&rdquo;或&ldquo;网络文化经营&rdquo;或&ldquo;信息技术服务&rdquo;等项目。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">知识服务为定向经营类目，在新增经营类目时需经审核后方可运营。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">只允许在数字内容-知识服务入驻的商家新增知识服务类目下的三级类目。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">不支持老商家变更主营类目或新增知识服务类目下的三级类目。</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 697.4pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"930\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.6pt; line-height: 21pt; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">旗舰店授权书模板：</span><a href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/926-4279.html\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">旗舰店授权书模板</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.6pt; line-height: 21pt; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">卖场店授权书模板：</span><a href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/1000-44485.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">卖场店授权模板</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.6pt; line-height: 21pt; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东开放平台各类目资费一览表：</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">京东开放平台类目资费规则</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.6pt; line-height: 21pt; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">店铺命名规则：</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">附则</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东商家的行为，发生在本管理规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本管理规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东可根据平台运营情况随时调整本管理规则并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有规定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无规定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本规则标准于2025年5月26日修订，于2025年6月2日生效。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</p>",
